<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.2">
<l>ilaṅkaip patikkaṉ ṟiṟaiyā yavarakkar</l>
<l>kulamkeṭ ṭavarmā ḷa<supplied>k</supplied>koṭip  puṭṭirittāy</l>
<l>vilaṅkal kuṭumit tiruvēṅ kaṭammēya</l>
<l>valaṅkal tuḷapam muṭiyā yaruḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who furled the bird banner, ruining the clan of the demon</l>
<l>Who became the leader of the city of Lanka so he died that day,</l>
<l>You with a tulasī garland crown who dwells</l>
<l>On the mountain peaks of Tiruvēṅkaṭam, be gracious!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
